des:
The purpose of this skill is an attempt to replicate the perspective of a real person by using state of the art machine learning models. It is also an attempt to scale up Gary Vee, which brings massive value to the community.

The attempt to replicate Gary Vee's way of thinking, all models were trained based on hundreds of hours of his publicly available videos, talks, and podcasts. All of the sample quotes in this skill were generated by using machine learning and not edited by a human to correct them.
